title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 25 2022
description:
Fantastic montage of our leaders incorrectly saying the covid shot would keep us from getting and spreading covid. Then they all got covid. Dr. Deborah Birx lied to the world for years: "I knew these vaccines were not going to protect against infection and I think we overplayed the vaccines." What are they lying about now? Pollster Frank Luntz: If Trump announces for president before 2022 election, he could cost Republicans the House and Senate. Airline pilots call in to discuss the many delays and cancellations.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
